collectionMetadata.name: Number of Members under CPF Investment Schemes as at end of Quarter
collectionMetadata.description: Number of members under CPF Investment Schemes (Ordinary and Special Account) as at end of quarter

datasetMetadata.name: Number of members under CPF Investment Schemes as at end of quarter
datasetMetadata.description:
For CPF Investment Scheme (Ordinary Account), the figures refer to members with investment account. However, they may or may not hold any investments in their accounts.
For CPF Investment Scheme (Special Account), the figures refer to members with investment holdings.
Figures are rounded to the nearest thousand.
